    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This chassis has been properly sorted for the long haul: the rear subframe has been reinforced, rod bearings have been replaced with VAC coated shells, and the dual-VANOS system has been completely overhauled with Beisan components. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with a limited-slip variable M differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension geometry remains sharp thanks to refreshed polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is in peak operational form, delivering a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience. This is a turn-key enthusiast build optimized for performance and reliability.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
